* Wed Apr 23 2026 Johan Hedin - 1.6.0 (not released yet)
- Code style cleanups
- Add test written by Claude Code
- Add purge command that removes expired certificates
- Add option to force clientAuth extension on signed certificates

* Mon Mar 30 2026 Johan Hedin - 1.5.3
- Support spaces in directory paths and filenames
- Code style cleanups
- Fix broken environment variable override for variables in settings.cfg

* Mon Mar 23 2026 Johan Hedin - 1.5.2
- Fix bug in the name print command
- Fix misspelled variable name
- Fix bad return value in internal exit trap

* Mon Mar 23 2026 Johan Hedin - 1.5.1
- Add name command that prints the Common Name of the CA

* Sun Mar 15 2026 Johan Hedin - 1.5.0
- Add support for non-interactive signing (--yes)
- Allow creating CSR with empty subject as long as SAN exist
- Use first SAN as CN when signing if subject in CSR is empty
- Ask for lifespan for CA, certs and CRL during CA creation
- Save cert and CRL lifespan as settings in a CA
- Add support for picking up CA settings from environment variables
- Add support for non-interactive creation of CA (--yes)
- Implement re-sign
- Bash completion enhancements

* Wed Jan 01 2025 Johan Hedin - 1.4.1
- Remove debug printout

* Wed Jan 01 2025 Johan Hedin - 1.4.0
- Support for older openssl. New min requirement is 1.0.1e
- 2048 bits as default RSA key size to support a wider user base
- Smart card documentation cleanups and clarifications
- Support for setting RSA key size for CA and CSR
- Initial support for RSASSA-PSS for CA and CSR creation
- Initial support for RSASSA-PSS when signing a CSR
- Added man page
- Added bash completion
- Added Makefile for install/uninstall

* Fri Feb 26 2021 Johan Hedin - 1.3.0
- Support for adding MS UPN SAN to personal CSR

* Sat Jul 18 2020 Johan Hedin - 1.2.0
- Support for key via PKCS11 URI (typically smartcard) when creating CSR

* Fri Jul 17 2020 Johan Hedin - 1.1.0
- Added support for personal CSRs (ask for GN, SN, UID and E-mail)

* Thu Jul 16 2020 Johan Hedin - 1.0.0
- First release
